a City\u2013Balboa]] (begins April 28, 2020)\n<!-- -->\n}}\n[[File:Puertas biom\u00e9tricas.jpg|thumb|Use of biometric doors at Jorge Chavez International Airport.]]\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport-dest-list\n|[[Atlas Air]]| [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[Avianca Cargo]]| [[El Dorado International Airport|Bogot\u00e1]], [[Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda C\u00f3rdova International Airport|Medellin-C\u00f3rdova]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[Cielos Airlines]]| [[Ministro Pistarini International Airport|Buenos Aires-Ezeiza]], [[Mexico City International Airport|Mexico City]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Mariscal Sucre International Airport (New)|Quito]]\n|[[KF Cargo]]| [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[Korean Air Cargo]]| [[Viracopos-Campinas International Airport|Campinas Viracopos]], [[Los Angeles International Airport|Los Angeles]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Incheon International Airport|Seoul-Incheon]]\n|[[LATAM Cargo Brasil]]| [[Viracopos-Campinas International Airport|Campinas Viracopos]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[LATAM Cargo Chile]]| [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[LATAM Cargo Colombia]]| [[Rio de Janeiro-Gale\u00e3o International Airport|Rio de Janeiro-Gale\u00e3o]]\n|[[LATAM Cargo Mexico]]| [[Viracopos-Campinas International Airport|Campinas Viracopos]], [[Mexico City International Airport|Mexico City]]\n|[[Lufthansa Cargo]]| [[Frankfurt Airport|Frankfurt]]\n|[[Martinair]]| [[Mariscal Sucre International Airport|Quito]]\n|[[Northern Air Cargo]] | [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]\n|[[Qatar Airways Cargo]]| [[Viracopos-Campinas International Airport|Campinas Viracopos]], [[Hamad International Airport|Doha]]\n|[[Sky Lease Cargo]]| [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol|Amsterdam]], [[Viracopos-Campinas International Airport|Campinas Viracopos]], [[Guaran\u00ed International Airport|Ciudad del Este]], [[El Dorado International Airport|Bogot\u00e1]], [[Ministro Pistarini International Airport|Buenos 