cuador}} [[Mariscal Sucre International Airport|Quito, Ecuador]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 399,307|| [[Avianca Ecuador]], [[LATAM Ecuador]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]], [[TAME]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|11|| {{flagicon|Dominican Republic}} [[Punta Cana International Airport|Punta Cana, Dominican Republic]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 285,775|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|12|| {{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol|Amsterdam, Netherlands]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 283,094|| [[KLM]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|13|| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Los Angeles International Airport|Los Angeles, United States]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 282,022|| [[LATAM Chile]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|14|| {{flagicon|El Salvador}} [[Monse\u00f1or \u00d3scar Arnulfo Romero International Airport|San Salvador, El Salvador]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 215,839|| [[Avianca El Salvador]], [[Avianca Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|15|| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[Carrasco International Airport|Montevideo, Uruguay]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 213,186|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|16|| {{flagicon|Bolivia}} [[El Alto International Airport|La Paz, Bolivia]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 200,961|| [[Avianca Ecuador]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]], [[Peruvian Airlines]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17|| {{flagicon|Cuba}} [[Jos\u00e9 Mart\u00ed International Airport|Havana, Cuba]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 186,326|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18|| {{flagicon|Ecuador}} [[Jos\u00e9 Joaqu\u00edn de Olmedo International Airport|Guayaquil, Ecuador]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 174,820|| [[Avianca Ecuador]], [[LATAM Ecuador]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\