[LATAM Paraguay]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|28|| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Ingeniero Aeron\u00e1utico Ambrosio L.V. Taravella International Airport|C\u00f3rdoba, Argentina]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 121,832|| [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|29|| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Dallas-Fort Worth International Airport|Dallas-Fort Worth, United States]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 120,643|| [[American Airlines]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|30|| {{flagicon|Canada}} [[Toronto-Pearson International Airport|Toronto-Pearson, Canada]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 120,610|| [[Air Canada Rouge]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|31|| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Governor Francisco Gabrielli International Airport|Mendoza, Argentina]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 109,484|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|32|| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Rosario \u2013 Islas Malvinas International Airport|Rosario, Argentina]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 101,990|| [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|33|| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Orlando International Airport|Orlando, United States]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{increase}} 100,983|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|34|| {{flagicon|Colombia}} [[Rafael N\u00fa\u00f1ez International Airport|Cartagena, Colombia]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 92,525|| [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|35|| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark, United States]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 85,269||[[United Airlines]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|36|| {{flagicon|Colombia}} [[Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda C\u00f3rdova International Airport|Medell\u00edn-JMC, Colombia]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{decrease}} 84,356|| [[Avianca Per\u00fa]], [[LATAM Per\u00fa]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align